# Dependency Injection

## Annotations

- `@injectable` — services, use cases, cubits
- `@singleton` — single-instance classes
- `@module` — external dependency modules
- **Must** regenerate after changes: `flutter pub run build_runner build --delete-conflicting-outputs`


## External Singletons

```dart
@module
abstract class FirebaseAuthModule {
  @singleton
  FirebaseAuth get firebaseAuth => FirebaseAuth.instance;
}
```

## Generated Files

- **Must not** manually edit `*.g.dart`, `*.mocks.dart`, `*.gen.dart`, `dependency_injection.module.dart`
- Fix issues in source files, then regenerate
- Use `flutter pub run build_runner clean` if regeneration doesn't pick up changes
